   ON THE FUTURE OF OUR
   EDUCATIONAL INSTITUTIONS
 
        *       *       *       *       *
 
 
 
 
   _FRIEDRICH NIETZSCHE_
 
   ON THE FUTURE OF OUR
   EDUCATIONAL INSTITUTIONS
 
 
 
   TRANSLATED, WITH INTRODUCTION, BY
   J.M. KENNEDY
 
 
 
 
   T.N. FOULIS
   13 & 15 FREDERICK STREET
