     4 See _Richard Wagner_, by Houston Stuart Chamberlain (translated by
       G. A. Hight), pp. 15, 16.
 
     5 Constable & Co., 1911.
 
     6 See Authors Preface to The Case of Wagner in this volume.
 
     7 Senta is the heroine in the Flying Dutchman_Tr._
 
     8 A character in Tannhauser._Tr_.
 
